textfsm_template:
Value SERVER (\S+)
Value SERVER_ADDRESS (\d{1,3}(?:\.\d{1,3}){3}#\d+)
Value NAME (\S+)
Value IPV4_ADDR (\d{1,3}(?:\.\d{1,3}){3})
Value IPV6_ADDR ([0-9a-fA-F:]+)

Start
  ^Server:\s+${SERVER}\s*$$
  ^Address:\s+${SERVER_ADDRESS}\s*$$
  ^Non-authoritative answer:\s*$$
  ^Name:\s+${NAME}\s*$$
  ^Address:\s+${IPV4_ADDR}\s*$$ -> Record
  ^Address:\s+${IPV6_ADDR}\s*$$ -> Record
